Package pt.uc.dei.annotations

package pt.uc.dei.annotations
  • Annotation Interfaces
    Class
    Description
    AdminOnly
    Annotation to indicate that a resource or method requires admin privileges.
    AdminSelfOrManager
    Annotation to indicate that a resource or method requires the user to be an admin, the resource owner (self), or a manager.
    AllowAnonymous
    Annotation to indicate that a resource or method allows anonymous (unauthenticated) access.
    AnotherOnly
    Annotation to indicate that a resource or method requires the user to be either the resource owner (self) or an admin.
    DirectManagerOnly
    Annotation to indicate that a resource or method requires direct manager privileges.
    ManagerOfUser
    Annotation to indicate that a resource or method requires the user to be the manager of the resource's user.
    ManagerOnly
    Annotation to indicate that a resource or method requires manager privileges.
    SelfOrAdminOnly
    Annotation to indicate that a resource or method requires the user to be either the resource owner (self) or an admin.
